Water Sort Puzzle - Color Sort
Privacy Policy
1. Introduction
Welcome to "Water Sort Puzzle - Color Sort" (referred to as "the Game"). We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you play the Game.
2. Information We Collect
Personal Information:
Since the Game does not require login or registration, we do not collect any personal information from you.
Non-Personal Information:
We may collect non-personal information related to your gameplay, such as game progress, preferences, and other in-game activity. This information is used to improve the Game and provide a better user experience.
3. Use of Information
The information collected is used solely for the purpose of:
Enhancing your gaming experience
Analyzing game performance and user engagement
Providing updates and improvements to the Game
4. Data Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure the security of your non-personal information. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
5. Third-Party Services
The Game does not include advertisements or third-party services. We do not share your information with third parties.
6. Children's Privacy
The Game is not directed towards children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected such information, we will take steps to delete it.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at
premiumqualityapps.com@gmail.com
.
